    <div class="c2r">
        <h2>A detailed look at schools on the list</h2>
        
        <p>The following data helps better understand each school. </p>
        
        <dl class="examples">
            <dt><img alt="" src="http://dummyimage.com/138" /> ISAT score trends by cohort</dt>
            <dd>
                <p>Math, Reading, and Science scores are shown for one group of students tracked through grades 3–8.</p>
                <p class="mute">Left: <a href="#">Ira F Aldridge Elementary School</a></p>
            </dd>
            
            <dt><img alt="" src="http://dummyimage.com/138" /> 5Essentials trends</dt>
            <dd>
                <p>The University of Chicago characterises successful schools as having five basic elements involving instruction, environment, families, leaders, and teachers.</p>
                <p class="mute">Left: <a href="#">Ira F Aldridge Elementary School</a></p>
            </dd>
            
            <dt><img alt="" src="http://dummyimage.com/138" /> Probation status trends</dt>
            <dd>
                <p>Schools scoring under a specified level are placed on academic probation which triggers administrative interventions aimed at improving performance.</p>
                <p class="mute">Left: <a href="#">Ira F Aldridge Elementary School</a></p>
            </dd>
            
            <dt><img alt="" src="http://dummyimage.com/138" /> Mobility rate trends</dt>
            <dd>
                <p>This is the percentage of students who move into, or out of, a school at times other than the beginning or end of a school year. These students may have difficulty keeping up academically.</p>
                <p class="mute">Left: <a href="#">Ira F Aldridge Elementary School</a></p>
            </dd>
            
            <dt><img alt="" src="http://dummyimage.com/138" /> Enrollment trends</dt>
            <dd>
                <p>A school’s enrollment trend is calculated based on student populations on the 20th day of each school year. This helps estimate future needs for space, personnel, equipment, etc.</p>
                <p class="mute">Left: <a href="#">Ira F Aldridge Elementary School</a></p>
            </dd>
        </dl>
